title: Link joins hands with the World Green Organisation to distribute over 2,300 surplus food packages ...
text: ( Source : The Link Real Estate Investment Trust ) The 'Linking Food with Love - From the Golden Age to the Greens ' Surplus Food Donation Project ' (the Project) celebrated its success at the closing ceremony and fair today at Stanley Plaza .
